      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SNOOPY'S ETHICS (4) was out of the placings last time when sixth at Wentworth Park (30.76) but scored three back at Bulli (22.97). Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Comes through a solid form race last start. Better than last start and worth following up. GO FORWARD JACKI (2) boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 1.75 lengths (18.38) behind Anjo Ruby at Richmond. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Bold showing expected. HAPPY ETHICS (3) turned in a plain effort last time when eighth at Wentworth Park over 520m behind Elsa Above (30.83) in a Grade 5. Placed at her previous run. The form from her last run stacks up well. Has ability and can atone. ZIPPER BANK (1) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
